f="https://www.nme.com/news/music/psychedelic-furs-and-waitresses-saxophonist-mars-williams-dies-aged-68-3545519">邮政迷幻的皮草和女服务员萨克斯管火星威廉姆斯死亡，现年68岁，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
这些流媒体服务在过去一年中删除了许多电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-streaming-serming-serming-serming-move-movies-load-movies-the-past-the-past--3545512?utm_source = rsss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign=负载电影超过一年Adam StarkeyTue, 21 Nov 2023 16:03:40 +0000 Film NewsNewsAmazon Prime VideoApple TV+Netflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3545512 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="派拉蒙" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据新数据，派拉蒙+一年中失去了近1,500个头衔</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-streaming-services-removed-load-movies-over-the-past-year-3545512">这些流媒体服务在过去一年中删除了许多电影，这</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现的。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="派拉蒙" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Paramount-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>新数字强调了过去一年中流媒体服务的广泛削减和增加，而派拉蒙+的下降幅度最差。</p><p>正如<a href="https://www.indiewire.com/news/analysis/paramount-plus-content-cuts-movies-1234927985/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Indiewire</em></a>报道的那样，最近的一项<a href="https://data.reelgood.com/counting-catalog-content-in-an-era-of-rising-prices-for-subscription-streaming-reelgoods-tally-of-library-titles-shows-which-services-are-maintaining-their-value-proposition-and-w/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reelgood Audit</a>介绍了美国八个领先流媒体服务的库，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">Amazon Prime Video</a> ，Peacock，Hulu，Hulu，Max， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney+</a> ，Paramount+， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paramount">Paramount+</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a> ，以评估他们过去两个年。</p><p>根据数据，Paramount+在2022年10月17日提供了2,302个电影冠军，该电影的电影已在2023年10月15日之前降至830部电影。这意味着电影库的下降了64％，在363范围内失去了1,472个标题。天。</p><p>但是，流媒体服务的电视目录增加了3％。 </p><figure id="attachment_3282879" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3282879" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3282879" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Batgirl-main.jpg" alt="蝙蝠女" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Batgirl-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Batgirl-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Batgirl-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Batgirl-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Batgirl-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Batgirl-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3282879" class="wp-caption-text">莱斯利·格雷斯（Leslie Grace）为“蝙蝠女”（Batgirl）信用：华纳兄弟（Warner Bros）。</figcaption></figure><p>麦克斯（Max）被称为HBO Max，是另一项流媒体服务。电影图书馆从2022年10月至2023年10月失去了390张冠军，从2,558部电影降至2,168部电影，下降了15％。但是，由于添加了Discovery+，电视库的大小几乎翻了一番。</p><p>拥有Max的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/looney-tunes-coyote-vs-acme-uncancelled-public-outcry-3537769"><em>华纳</em></a>兄弟<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/batgirl-shelved-warner-bros-will-not-receive-theatrical-or-streaming-release-3282047"><em>（</em></a> Warner Bros. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/looney-tunes-coyote-vs-acme-uncancelled-public-outcry-3537769"><em>Acme</em></a> 。</p><p>同时，其他流媒体服务仅增长。孔雀和胡鲁的增长最大，前者的电影图书馆在2022年至2023年之间增长了47％，而Hulu则增加了一倍。迪士尼+添加了154部电影，亚马逊Prime视频增长了17％，Netflix看到了56部电影，而Apple TV+增长了11部电影。</p><p> Netflix<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-just-cancelled-these-five-tv-shows-3541221">本月初在一次席卷中取消了五场演出</a>，其中包括<em>Shadow and Bone</em> ， <em>Glamior</em> ， <em>Elvis Elvis</em> ， <em>Farzar</em>和<em>Fall上尉</em>。</p><p>演出取消后，粉丝们竞选了Shadow和Bone，由另一个流媒体服务挑选，请愿<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/fan-petition-to-save-shadow-and-bone-reaches-over-120000-signatures-3544483">书积累了120,000多个签名</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-streaming-services-removed-load-movies-over-the-past-year-3545512">这些流媒体服务在过去一年中删除了许多电影，这</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现的。</p> ;
